DataElementConcept.preferredName: Endometrial Mixed Cell Adenocarcinoma Histologic Subtype
DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: An adenocarcinoma that arises from the endometrium and is characterized by the presence of both type I and type II endometrial adenocarcinoma components.
